{title: Be Still, My Soul}
{subtitle: Katharina von Schlegel (1752) / tr. Jane Borthwick (1855) / Finlandia tune}
{key: Eb}
{time: 4/4}
{tempo: 72}
{comment: Set to Sibelius's Finlandia (1899). The Japanese hymn やすかれわがこころよ (笹渕友一 tr.) uses the same melody, but its translation remains under copyright.}

{start_of_verse: 1}
